item.title: Fixing the 289 cache!
item.dc:creator: @CoonHunter CoonHunter
item.description:
@CoonHunter wrote:

[quote=“badger41, post:5, topic:353313”][quote author=CoonHunter link=topic=449640.msg3298872#msg3298872 date=1281140560]

Emotes, sprites, animations and models are missing from mine.

For models, was the look updated since 317? If not, then just search ‘Graffle’ in the downloads section, he has a topic in there of a completely un-packed 317 or 377 cache, I forget which. That might help you with some of the fixing, but not all.
[/quote]

the only thing i would think would be different is the platebody inv models, in 289 i think they still had gloves attached to them.[/quote]
Possible, I will do some poking around and see what I can find out
